{
  "stem": "10588.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he bought most of the merchandise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he left-- it didn't take long-- the same men came with the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He denounced us and brought them to our home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because all the others he didn't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they started to interrogate my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who is the man?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the first time, in my presence at least, that I heard my mother lying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because at that time, we already realized that they use something that if one would do something wrong, they would destroy the whole family, sometimes punish everybody, one for all.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother realized that if she's going to tell, that they're going to kill the whole family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they broke the laws imposed by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she continued to say she doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They interrogate her for a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they saw that they're not getting any place with her, that she is resisting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took her to the police station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were you in the same room with her when this was going on?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Listen, when they took my mother, I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I already knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a 13-year-old girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I already saw what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw that they're not our friends and not the same Nazis-- Germans that my grandmother used to talk about.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I followed her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they kept on chasing me away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And finally, one of them got a bright idea, said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see, that's why it was useful that I spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could understand what they said more, because it's similar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And mostly during the Holocaust, I could follow all this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that saved me from a lot of beating.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us both.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
